@startuml Album Organization Sequence
!theme plain

actor User
participant UI
participant API
participant CommandHandler
participant AlbumAggregate
participant Events

== Create Album ==
User -> UI: Create new album
UI -> API: POST /api/albums
API -> CommandHandler: CreateAlbumCommand
CommandHandler -> AlbumAggregate: Create album
AlbumAggregate --> CommandHandler: Album created
CommandHandler -> Events: Publish AlbumCreated
CommandHandler --> API: AlbumDto
API --> UI: 201 Created
UI --> User: Show new album

== Add Photos to Album ==
User -> UI: Add photos to album
UI -> API: POST /api/albums/{id}/photos
API -> CommandHandler: AddPhotosToAlbumCommand
CommandHandler -> AlbumAggregate: Add photos
AlbumAggregate --> CommandHandler: Photos added
CommandHandler -> Events: Publish PhotoAddedToAlbum (each)
CommandHandler --> API: Success
API --> UI: 200 OK
UI --> User: Photos added notification

@enduml
